So my question for you is, what are your countdown
traditions, and if you have one of these Advent

00:03:56.340 --> 00:04:00.020
calendars, weren’t you ever tempted to skip
a few days ahead

00:04:00.020 --> 00:04:01.900
and eat more chocolate than you should?

